Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動總司令他…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他留下了一張字條
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎今天一早就離開了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去尋找傳說中的神話型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有什麼線索了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聖之書裡或許有所記載
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聖之書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有這麼多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個還真是夠深的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這之前還超活躍的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 安迪挖出來的溫泉真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼頭緒嗎 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,================OP===============
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:32.67,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:39.87,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:55.52,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:05.99,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:18.07,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:28.66,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:34.82,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:40.67,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:45.04,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.38,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.39,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.11,0:01:32.67,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:39.87,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:55.52,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:05.99,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:18.07,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:28.66,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:34.82,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:40.67,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:45.04,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:48.38,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.39,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,================OP===============
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音樂會?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要只是考慮 真的陪我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你答覆 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是約會的邀請嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變形象之後變得備受歡迎了啊 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再甜一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在模擬戰時的大膽告白可能也起到了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給人以爽朗大方的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 是不是因為我之前說了些多餘的話你才…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是 只是想說就說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少比之前也有所進展了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這前方又是死巷子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴白同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:03:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正要送信到宿舍樓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這封是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 其實這也沒什麼好隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸寄來了一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和他相處得不怎麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以真沒想到能收到他的信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是會關心我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了 畢竟是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話由我來說會不會很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的事我還記得一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但父親的事我就完全不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 我也還有很多事情弄不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我袒護他的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請原諒這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不是想責怪御子乃你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為現在是大家必須齊心協力的關鍵時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的使命是讓大家團結一心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我真的不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真少見啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的信錯寄給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒看清楚就拆開了封口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為老爸的字太難認了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 這年頭不用寄信也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 那信件就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道為什麼Neo DEAVA要接納御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我在擔心她是否會成為你的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這女兒從小做就什麼事都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以將她從Neo DEAVA帶回來然後安置在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對爸爸來說 我還是一如既往地一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很擔心安迪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在非常消沉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你們兩個一直都很要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前遠足的時候 發生了點事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂得叫別人好好說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一輪到自己卻沒有跨出那一步的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總會不禁地把其他男人看成跟我父親一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽說過我討厭男人的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和父親相處得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖泥帶水的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我一直在對父親察言觀色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有話想說 也因為害怕被訓斥而一直說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是又被責罵不夠爽快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.92,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是父親 也終歸是異性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的想法只有男人自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說修修是公的還是母的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,訓練到這麼晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起自己是一個女戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然最近有點莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不希望連這一長處也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死巷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運作率一片低迷 已經低破40%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大的問題是次元轉移所耗能量過多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果繼續前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至會影響到市民最低限度的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計屆時會引發大規模的暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了山窮水盡的地步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到神樂的下落了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分抱歉 他依然下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕又是未影從中穿針引線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人從未考慮過Altair的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好Afra Gnis的出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我親自前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是時候要感受一下久違的戰場之上的氛圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓這世界再度響起嬰兒的啼哭聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找到真實的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定還能遇到被你留在Vega的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是要責怪你讀信的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是看你很失落的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼當父母的總愛瞎操心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我成為了怪炎和大家的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一事無成的我還不如老老實實待在家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你從小就對人過分地察言觀色了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想觸怒或傷害對方 因而害怕說出自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實你最害怕的是自己受到傷害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直認為你是一事無成的膽小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有個人在和我初次見面的時候就這麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我跟她相識不久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得現在的御子乃並不是你所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信御子乃也一定希望在今後能有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔他說過這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不爽 但正如他所說 你的確變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想讓老爸也看看現在的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次聽到這樣的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉穩而高貴的聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人懷念的蔚藍（青澀）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那青春的Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲 事到如今你終於要大展宏圖了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說 你是去尋找花朵所留下的種子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不曾見過的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充斥著敵人老大的派頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太慢了 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒什麼大不了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這種地方也要挖洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 現在的他不能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠出擊的Vector有五機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用兩架Vector來支援Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊的Element是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎 阿馬塔 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 不能讓你們出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被禁止戰鬥的話 我將不再是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想作為一名戰士 超越作為女人的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想為大家出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓男生們持續作戰也確實是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動 我的決定沒有錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 AQUARION由阿馬塔 婕希卡和諸井搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎和MIX從旁支援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡那傢伙異常地焦急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此才令人分外擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總有種很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合體吧 機首是我 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心碎合體 GO AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少在戰鬥的時候能在阿馬塔身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是婕希卡的情感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然合體什麼的最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION GEPART
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量產機就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因為是Vector就把我們看扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一擊定勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太青澀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我很欣賞你那氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直完全無效
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報告損害情況
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西區綜合體育館一帶遭到破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人將GEPART的光線吸收後成倍奉還了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在Altair已經看不到這般年少輕狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但光憑那樣是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要衝動 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮擊戰風險太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是進行格鬥戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不用你說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸井 借你的力量給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超捻轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱力還真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不論在哪個時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的都是年輕的那一方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了避免無意義的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓你們見識一下絕對的戰力差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超捻轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一招對我不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEPART被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把合體解除了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諸井因剛才的衝擊失去了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Y現正自動航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Element替換 御子乃出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎和阿馬塔、御子乃合體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡從旁支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的你欠缺冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼那麼急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 怪炎 我們合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人正向這邊靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺Abductor的行動不是以攻擊為目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人侵入了我們的通信線路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vega的諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Altair的最高領導人出雲?神呂木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你們的指揮官進行交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說最高領導人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫克蕾雅·多露西娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是Neo Deava的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指揮官也是Igler…是女性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女性不是大多都不喜歡爭鬥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實可以這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在一定情況和場合下 女性反而更為強悍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為某些緣故我們需要最強的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最強的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想給此地帶來災害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能將Rare·Igler接到我們的世界去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們怎麼能答應你這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果雙方有開啟談判的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動在這裡的話他會怎樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡的Vector正在向Abductor移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你們需要女人 我就跟你們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來就能改變現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rare·Igler反應!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 你別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多加珍惜自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你只是在自暴自棄而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看出那個Rare·Igler有投降的意願
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕獲她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾隨合體 GO AQUARION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUARION EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛翔的機械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在操縱它的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認一下如何 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的雙眼好好確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會出現這種幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔的心之弦正在被什麼人撥弄著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清澈、甘甜而苦澀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是未影的把戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.89,0:21:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愛耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但機械天使確實停止了行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有錯的 那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 大敵當前…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不會讓婕希卡你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要衝動 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.00,0:21:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限拳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有翅膀的孩子啊 我們後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…她代替我被…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIX
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MIX!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:58.38,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:06.19,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:16.17,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:25.67,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:33.53,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:41.12,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:45.31,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:48.47,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:53.00,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:56.21,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:24:00.54,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:07.05,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:58.38,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 點綴著雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:06.19,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}從睡夢中驚醒之後 遠望著憂傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:16.17,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這份青澀的感覺 依存在綠葉錯綜的紋路之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:25.67,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}側耳聆聽 晨露緩緩落下的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:33.53,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所創造的這個世界並不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:41.12,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因為這裡每天都有戀情一段接一段地告終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:45.31,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初嘗戀愛的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:48.47,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這個你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:53.00,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不見天日也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:56.21,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:24:00.54,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘卻也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:07.05,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很討厭膽小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.07,0:24:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也許正因為畏懼 才能毫不猶豫的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在向前邁進一步是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 第一次重逢
